			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repro steps:\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. Trigger attack on Den and resolve it (goto 210.35, 26.58, 402.82, advance on the Den and use killcombat)\r\n4. Trigger Aradin and Zevlor situation and resolve it without a fight (goto 205.71, 31.09, 480.66 and use Shift-Q on persuasion check).\r\n5. goto 166.38, 19.85, 543.64\r\n6. Talk with Aradin."
				},
